headline: M&T Bank Corporation Announces First Quarter 2025 Earnings Release and Conference Call
summary: M&T Bank Corporation ("M&T") (NYSE: MTB) plans to announce its first quarter 2025 earnings results in a press release that will be issued before the market opens on Monday, April 14, 2025.
